#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/projections.rst:44
msgid ""
"To change the projection for a 3D View, choose the :menuselection:`View "
"--> Orthographic` or the :menuselection:`View --> Perspective` menu "
"entry. The :kbd:`Numpad5` shortcut toggles between the two modes. "
"Changing the projection for a 3D View does not affect the way the scene "
"will be rendered. Rendering is in perspective by default. If you need to "
"create an orthographic rendering, select the camera, go to the Camera "
"tab and press the *Orthographic* button in the *Lens* panel."
msgstr ""
"要更改3D视图的投影, 请选择 :menuselection:`视图 --> 正交视图` 或者 :"
"menuselection:`视图 --> 透视视图` 菜单项. 使用快捷键 :kbd:`Numpad5` 在两"
"种模式之间切换.改变3D视图的投影并不会影响到场景的渲染方式. 默认情况下，是"
"在透视视图下渲染的。 如果你需要创建一个正交渲染, 选择摄相机， 到相机标签"
"页， 在 *镜头* 面板选择 *正交* 按钮。"

